  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or CAP 698 figure 4.8. <br /> \rAn MRJT aircraft is intending to perform a flight from an airport with the data shown below. Calculate the V<strong><sub>1</sub></strong>, V<strong><sub>R</sub></strong> and V<strong><sub>2</sub></strong> for this take off.</p>\r\r<p>Runway: 01 <br /> \rPressure Altitude: 328 ft <br /> \rSlope: 1% Upslope <br /> \rOAT: 0\u00b0 <br /> \rW/V: 190\u00b0/10 kt <br /> \rTake off mass: 61 430 kg <br /> \rFlaps 5</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<p>V<sub>1</sub>: 145 kt; V<sub>R</sub>: 149 kt; V<sub>2</sub>: 156 kt</p>",
    "b": "<p>V<sub>1</sub>: 146 kt; V<sub>R</sub>: 150 kt; V<sub>2</sub>: 157 kt</p>",
    "c": "<p>V<sub>1</sub>: 145 kt; V<sub>R</sub>: 150 kt; V<sub>2</sub>: 157 kt</p>",
    "d": "<p>V<sub>1</sub>: 147 kt; V<sub>R</sub>: 151 kt; V<sub>2</sub>: 158 kt</p>"
  },
